profile:
At Hometurf Lawn Care, we have been treating the lawns of our loyal customers for over 30 years. As a family-owned and -operated business, we have grown by delivering lush, healthy, green lawns while using only the highest quality products applied by professional lawn care technicians. Let us help you make your lawn look its best this season!

Our season-long lawn care programs take the guess work out of which products to use and when. Applications are scheduled to be applied four to six weeks apart throughout the season for optimal turf care. We strive to ensure everything your lawn needs is included in our programs. No telemarketing or sales calls pushing unnecessary extras.

Our services include: lawn care programs, lawn maintenance programs, fertilizer, weed control, insect control, aeration, grass seeding, dethatching, top dressing, chinch bug control and grub control.

profile:
“A business big enough to do the job, but small enough to care.”

Klink & Son is a family-run property maintenance company, based in Stoney Creek, ON, providing landscaping, property maintenance & snow removal services in Hamilton, Grimsby & surrounding areas.
Established in 1996, Klink and Son specializes in lawn and property maintenance in both residential and commercial properties.
landscaping hamilton ontario 

Klink and Son are owned and operated by Paul and Nick Klingender and primarily work out of the Hamilton/Stoney Creek area. Feel free to call us today to schedule a customized maintenance program that will meet your specific needs.

We are family owned and operated and take pride in maintaining 100% customer satisfaction. The two pillars of our exceptional customer satisfaction rests on delivering Quality Services and overall Dependability to get the job done right, the first time.

Contact our landscapers at Klink & Son
Klink & Son Property Maintenance is located in Stoney Creek, Ontario and serves the Greater Hamilton Area including Burlington, Waterdown, Ancaster, Aldershot, Dundas and Grimsby. Call us today to see how we can manage your residential or commercial property.
